<plot>Mateo and Luigi are vying for Lena's affections. Mateo peeks into Lena's window, and is chased off as a peeping Tom. Meanwhile, Luigi sends her a passionate letter but forgets to put an address on it. When Lena finds out about the peeping, she beats up Mateo. Luigi witnesses the beating and takes back his love letter from the dead letter office.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?552284</url></doc>
